                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <p>
                    Hardtop Road Trip!: With winter approaching, I was making a dilligent search to find a factory OEM hardtop. Hardtops provide
                    superior sound and heat insulation, and the completely transform the look of the car! However, these tops are tricky to find
                    locally and for a fair price. After several months of searching, I found a company based in the UK that exports hardtops to the US.
                    I had to wait several months for it to arrive, but I finally took delivery of my hardtop in Grand Junction, CO!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mt-5">
