            <div class="col-md-4">
                <p>
                    The cipher steering wheel is one of my favorite OEM+ upgrades to date. While the old factory steering wheel was rather
                    slippery and worn, the cipher wheel is much thicker and offers superior grip. The materials are high quality and the wheel
                    manages to maintain the airbag, which was an important saftey feature for me.
                </p>
